    Log Tree

    Replace Android Log in order to have custom logging messages and redirect the output to file
    Since:
    2018-04-12 

     
 Timber.plant(new LogTree());
 Timber.v("hello");
 Timber.d("hello");
 Timber.i("hello");
 Timber.w("hello");
 Timber.e("hello");
    Version:
    0.0
    Author:
    Patrick Richer St-Onge, Justine Pepin, Fabrice Charbonneau
